<section id="about" class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-b from-neutral-50 to-white">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Section Title -->
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-8 text-center">
        About <span class="text-brand-primary-600">Us</span>
      </h2>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="space-y-6 text-neutral-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p class="text-xl">
          AI is genuinely useful. But somewhere between “this changes everything” and “this is all overblown,” most people are just trying to figure out what to actually *do*.
        </p>
        <p>That’s where we come in.</p>

        <p>
          We focus on practical, real-world AI. Not hype, not fear, and not engineering workshops. Just clear, grounded ways to understand what AI can do and how to use it without becoming a technical expert or pretending you already are one.
        </p>

        <p>
          We’ve worked with teams who are asking honest questions: Where does this actually help? What’s worth ignoring? And how do we move forward without making things more complicated?
        </p>

        <p>Those are the right questions. We help you find the right answers.</p>
      </div>

